==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: mango tree
<hw>mango tree</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An East Indian tree of the genus
<gen>Mangifera</gen> (<spn>Mangifera Indica</spn>), related to the
cashew and the sumac. It grows to a large size, and produces a large
oval smooth-skinned fruit which is the <prod>mango</prod> of commerce.
It is now cultivated in tropical America.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mangoldwurzel</ent>⟦br⟧
